ACS’s Perez Seeks Investors in China, Confidencial Reports

-- B y   S h a r o n   S m y t h
-- 
2011-06-27T05:44:04Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-27/acs-s-perez-seeks-investors-in-china-confidencial-reports.html
Actividades de Construccion y
Servicios SA’s chief executive officer, Florentino Perez,
traveled to  China  recently in search of Chinese investors to
participate in business ventures,  El Confidencial  reported,
citing unidentified people in banking.  ACS is looking for investors to collaborate in its quest
for control of  Iberdrola SA (IBE)  and to provide capital that will
enable the company to bid for Spanish airport concessions, the
newspaper said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Sharon Smyth in Madrid at 
 ssmyth2@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editors responsible for this story:
Andrew Blackman at   ablackman@bloomberg.net  